I came here for a beautiful music – as believe its God’s Gifts and however ended up getting disgusted by comments that has turned even this into a political propaganda to divide people.

Before, I leave just a clarification (few bitter truths) for people fighting Pakistan vs India and Hindu vs Muslims
1) Pakistan vs India: Indian Sub-continent includes – Current India, Pakistan, Afghanistan, Bangladesh, Burma, Sri Lanka, Nepal – In Ancient Times, collectively called as Bharat. The phenomenon of Pakistan created on Religious line was the biggest curse on Sub-continent – based on Divide and Rule Policy. Cultural Thread of all this place is nearly the same with regional variation and that’s the reason we cant help admiring each other – though most time its disguised.

2) Hindu vs Muslims: Please remember that you might profess any religion now, however all our ancestors were Hindus. Most Muslims believe that they are off-springs of Arab Islamic Invaders – whereas the truth is most are forcible converts. This is so painful – that most pretend to ignore this fact and disguise themselves as Radical Islamists (even so most Arabs don’t respect Muslims from this continent and just think of them as tools to use for Arab Supremacy). Remember in the Movie Amar, Akbar, Anthony – the name of the father of these Characters is Ramlal – well that’s the truth of Indian Sub-continent too, recognise the fact & move on.

3) Kashmiri Freedom Struggle: The greatest genocide committed in Kashmir – by Raping, Maiming, Butchering Kashmiri Pundits by Islamic Supremist and then disguising it as Freedom Struggle is the biggest farce pushed un to face of the World. The Kashmiri Pundits still live a Refugees in their own land. Their crime they were Hindus and Kashmir had to be cleansed of them to show Muslim Majority. Remember the last King of Kashmir was a Hindu and he too was let down by his Muslim Prime Minister. He ceded to India when Pakistan invaded his Kingdom and try to overtake it as it did with Baluchistan. There is nothing called as IoK, there is only PoK and that was fault of a spineless Nehru. Kashmir will be within India with or without the Islamists. 

Lastly, remember all of the events / propaganda is meant to occupy people mind and heart with hate, and they cant see that they are being manipulated by leaders of this propaganda – so that the leaders and their family can lead a life of luxury in safety and perpetuate their rule – while people are busy fighting and killing each other. Remember Trio of Nehru, Jinnah & Gandhi – split the Nation to grab Power, the Price of which we are paying today.

Please keep Music out of the Propaganda. Post comments if you want to appreciate the beauty of the music and let it unify rather than divide. And one Rule for me: Never to read comments again.
